{"tid":291987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：不能承諾沒人會因主張自決或港獨被捕","createTime":"2017-06-21T04:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T06:13:21.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8542e08c3c74e92616654ae1e33b83618a34f32","tid":291987,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:01:06.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】候任行政長官林鄭月娥接受英國廣播公司訪問時說，不能承諾在任期內沒有人會因主張自決或港獨被捕。<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司的訪問以「香港新領袖?」為題，問到林鄭月娥以777票當選，如何有足夠認受性帶領香港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說不是票數的問題，而是正當性的問題，如果有人認為她當選是因為親北京力量，而把她當作北京的傀儡，就是無視她過去36年為香港所做的事。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又被問到可否承諾，在任內不會有人因為主張自決或港獨被捕。林鄭月娥說，在未知實際情況下不能作承諾，只是說會按法治辦事。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，每個人都有表達意見的自由，但言論會否觸犯法例，就要視乎法律條文。"},{"pid":"d4aa49899a8dff0cbd7e4259b35502802eb1243a","tid":291987,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:01:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/CARRIE.BBC.1030.2106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FCARRIE.BBC.1030.2106.jpg&h=438ef797&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"909316d6f3af075116ee677d4b33cd523d0e062a","tid":291987,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:02:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=225596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D225596&d=JydjAett6ydDo5rJC82wthFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=7ea7103c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D225596&h=e316976d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=225596</a>"},{"pid":"5f5f09adec55e81f9b84de82bcb66cef5e6217f0","tid":291987,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"